    <article class="h-entry">
        <div class="content row">
            <div class="post-container">
                <div class="col-12 col-sm-12 col-md-6 col-lg-6 col-xl-6">
                    <div>
                        <div class="page-title text-uppercase text-center p-name">
                            <a class="u-url" href="/blog/cheatsheet-imagemagick">Cheatsheet - ImageMagick</a>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-center">
                            By <a class="p-author h-card" href="https://varunbarad.com">Varun Barad</a> on <time class="post-date dt-published" datetime="Sun Oct 17 2021 00:00:00 GMT+0530 (India Standard Time)">October 17, 2021</time>
                        </div>
                        <div class="post-content e-content"><h2>Resize images to specific target size while padding remaining space with transparency</h2>
<pre><code class="language-shell">convert -auto-orient -background &quot;#00000000&quot; original.jpg -resize 720x576 -gravity center -extent 720x576 resized.png
</code></pre>
<h2>Resize all images of a file-type inside a folder</h2>
<pre><code class="language-shell">for PHOTO in *.jpg
do
    convert -auto-orient -background &quot;#00000000&quot; &quot;$PHOTO&quot; -resize 720x576 -gravity center -extent 720x576 &quot;resized/$PHOTO.png&quot;
done
</code></pre>
<h2>Replace a color in image with different color</h2>
<pre><code class="language-shell">convert input.png -fuzz 90% -fill &quot;#628FDB&quot; -opaque &quot;#000000&quot; star_blue.png
</code></pre>
<ul>
<li><code>fuzz</code>: Percentage matching of the color</li>
<li><code>opaque</code>: Color to replace</li>
<li><code>fill</code>: Color to replace with</li>
</ul>
<h2>Reverse the RGB colors in an image</h2>
<pre><code class="language-shell">convert input.png -channel RGB -negate output.png
</code></pre>
<h2>Resize image and then crop center to fit target size</h2>
<pre><code class="language-shell">convert original.jpg -resize 720x576^ -gravity center -crop 720x576+0+0 +repage resized.png
</code></pre>
<p>Automation is exciting ðŸ¤–</p>
